# ED 101


## Self-Compassion

- Self-Kindness
- Mindfulness
- Common Humanity

## Behaviors

- Avoidance of Sensations
- Fear of Aversive Consequences
- Disinterest in food
- Restriction of food groups
- Binging/Over-eating
- Purging
- Laxatives/Diuretics (The SHITS - Stupid, Horrible, Impulsive, Taking of, Stimulants)
- Over-exercising/compulsive-impulsive exertion
- Restriction due to scarcity mindset/lack of resources
- Orthorexia Behaviors
- Rumination
- Non-food eating disorder behaviors

## Diagnostics and Criteria

- Common EDs
- ARFID
- OSFED/UFED
- Pica

## Body Image

- Body Dysmorphia
- Body Dysphoria (Trans-specific)
- Body Checking - behavior
- Body Neutrality
- Avoidance of public spaces
- Body flaunting

## Comorbid Disorders

- Substance Abuse
- OCD
- ADHD
- Autism
- Depression
- Anxiety
- BPD
- Dissociation
- PTSD / C-PTSD
